@startuml Prettier_Composite_Fixed_Spaced

title Composite Pattern in Prettier (Modello GoF)

skinparam backgroundcolor ffffff
skinparam defaultFontName "Arial"
skinparam classAttributeIconSize 0
skinparam shadowing false

' --- SPAZIATURA ESTREMA E LINEE ORTOGONALI ---
skinparam nodesep 130
skinparam ranksep 130
skinparam linetype ortho

' --- STILI COORDINATI ---
skinparam class {
    BackgroundColor<<Client>> #E6F3FF
    BorderColor<<Client>> #438dd5
    BackgroundColor<<Component>> #F5F5F5
    BorderColor<<Component>> #707070
    BackgroundColor<<Node>> #85bbf0
    BorderColor<<Node>> #438dd5
}

' --- ENTITÀ E RUOLI ---

class "Rendering Engine" as RenderClient <<Client>>

class "Doc" as DocComponent <<Component>> {
  + evaluateLayout()
  + add(Doc)
  + remove(Doc)
  + getChild()
}

class "Leaf\n(String, Line Break)" as LeafNode <<Node>> {
  + evaluateLayout()
}

class "Composite\n(Group, Indent, Align)" as CompositeNode <<Node>> {
  + evaluateLayout()
  + add(Doc)
  + remove(Doc)
  + getChild()
}

' --- RELAZIONI GOF ---

' Il Client invoca l'interfaccia comune
RenderClient -right-> DocComponent

' Ereditarietà allungata (3 trattini invece di 2 per dare più respiro verticale)
DocComponent <|--- LeafNode
DocComponent <|--- CompositeNode

' Trucco: linea nascosta per forzare la spaziatura orizzontale
LeafNode -[hidden]right- CompositeNode

' Aggregazione che esce verso DESTRA prima di salire, creando un percorso pulito a "L"
CompositeNode o-right- "0..*" DocComponent : " child "

@enduml